### WineMarket Deploy Smoke — 10 requests
### Run: curl -f "{{base_url}}/wines" || exit 1

### Wine catalog
GET {{base_url}}/wines

### Wine filter
GET {{base_url}}/wines?region=Moravia

### Wine detail
GET {{base_url}}/wines/{{first_wine_id}}

### Products
GET {{base_url}}/products

### Product detail
GET {{base_url}}/products/{{first_product_id}}

### Shops
GET {{base_url}}/shops

### Shop detail
GET {{base_url}}/shops/1

### Events
GET {{base_url}}/events

### Winemaker profile
GET {{base_url}}/winemakers/1

### Health
GET {{base_url}}/health
